title: Peuple_Migrateur - XVID - d_mansen
description:
Title: Le Peuple Migrateur (2001) aka The Great Flying or The Migratory People
XVID Video and MP3 VBR Audio Codecs
Brief Narration and Subtitles in English

Gorgeously photographed documentary on migratory birds all over the world.  Despite the lack of commentary/narration, there are still strong narrative elements and continuity throughout.  The images and sounds of the birds themselves do indeed speak for themselves.  This is a most refreshing change from nature documentaries that try to explain every little thing about animal behavior, some going even to the length of anthropomorphizing animals by dubbing in human voices to speak for them.  I&#039;ve watched this movie numerous times and have not yet tired of it.  I&#039;m not even much of an animal or nature lover.
